      <p class="who-wall-text who-wall-text-left">I help high-ticket sales coaches and saas founders sell their offers to the people who want to build a better career, time flexibility and slowly make their way towards financial freedom, through carefully and human crafted content and funnels.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="who-wall-wrap who-wall-right">
      <div class="who-triangle who-triangle-right"></div>
<p class="who-wall-text who-wall-text-right">Because the kind of offer that's sole mission is to reshape someone's career path or impact their financial wellbeing is best to be demonstrated through human writing that will allow us to stand out from a market abusing AI generic writing.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── SERVICES ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="services" class="services-section">
