        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon-wrap"><span class="service-icon-ring"></span><Icon name="lucide:pen-tool" class="service-icon" /></div>
          <h3 class="service-card-title">Copywriting</h3>
          <p class="service-card-text">I rely on my own writing and communication skills to write your copies from web pages, emails and scripts. I don't use AI in my copywriting unless if it's for research and fixing grammar.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon-wrap"><span class="service-icon-ring"></span><Icon name="lucide:scroll-text" class="service-icon" /></div>
