        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon-wrap"><span class="service-icon-ring"></span><Icon name="lucide:layout" class="service-icon" /></div>
          <h3 class="service-card-title">Webpages</h3>
          <p class="service-card-text">Besides the writing part, I'll handle building a fully functional, ready-to-use landing page or sales page and connected directly to Google Analytics for performance tracking.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon-wrap"><span class="service-icon-ring"></span><Icon name="lucide:workflow" class="service-icon" /></div>
          <h3 class="service-card-title">Funnel Creation</h3>
          <p class="service-card-text">Depending on your offer and the goal you wanna achieve, I'll create the suitable funnel for your offer from the moment they click the ads to the part where they become your buyers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon-wrap"><span class="service-icon-ring"></span><Icon name="lucide:search-check" class="service-icon" /></div>
          <h3 class="service-card-title">Copy Audit</h3>
          <p class="service-card-text">I'll audit your copies and funnels and provide you feedbacks on what could be done better and which are to improve (and by audit I mean my own audit, not AI).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
