          <h3 class="service-card-title">Email Marketing</h3>
          <p class="service-card-text">I'll set up your CRM system (in case you haven't set one already) and write your email campaigns while making sure they don't end up in the spam folders.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      </div><!-- end carousel-track-wrap -->
    </div>
